OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers moving away southeastward this
OL,7,Fevening as clearer, dry conditions
OL,8,Ffollow from the northwest. This will
OL,9,Fleave lengthy clear spells overnight,
OL,10,Fleading to a chilly start to Saturday.
OL,11,FBreezy this evening but winds becoming
OL,12,Flight overnight.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FCloudy through the morning
OL,15,Fwith patchy light rain at times. Drier
OL,16,Fthrough the afternoon, with some
OL,17,Fbrighter spells. Winds strengthening
OL,18,Flater, strong inland with coastal
OL,19,Fgales into the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
