OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds Sunday morning slowly easing,
OL,7,Ffollowed by the odd blustery shower
OL,8,Ffrom the west. Sunshine and lighter
OL,9,Fwinds Monday; breezier Tuesday but
OL,10,Fstaying dry and sunny. Becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
